WEBVTT

00:03.477 --> 00:08.263
In Saudi Arabia, the royal family announces a new Islamic military alliance...

00:08.479 --> 00:11.502
...made up of 34 countries to fight terrorism.

00:11.943 --> 00:15.135
In Switzerland, the United Nations-sponsored peace talks...

00:15.456 --> 00:19.673
...aimed at finding a settlement to the conflict in Yemen open in Geneva.

00:21.129 --> 00:26.711
In Russia, Secretary of State John Kerry tells Russian President Vladimir Putin in Moscow...

00:27.029 --> 00:29.823
...that Russia and the United States can work together...

00:30.001 --> 00:32.568
...to make progress in ending the war in Syria.

00:36.219 --> 00:39.809
In the US, all public schools across Los Angeles, California...

00:40.020 --> 00:42.928
...were closed Tuesday due to a "credible threat."

00:45.368 --> 00:46.811
And finally from the Vatican,...

00:47.103 --> 00:50.751
...Pope Francis calls on governments to review their laws on migration...

00:51.004 --> 00:55.164
...in order to welcome refugees and help them integrate into society.

